void testConstructor() {

    assertEquals("Title", book.getTitle());
    assertEquals("Author", book.getAuthor());

    assertEquals("ISBN", book.getIsbn());

        • @Test: testSetters

@Test
void testSetters() {
    book = new Book("", "", "", "");
    book.setTitle("Title");
    book.setAuthor("Author");
    book.setYear("Year");
    book.setIsbn("ISBN");
    assertEquals("Title", book.getTitle());
    assertEquals("Author", book.getAuthor());
    assertEquals("Year", book.getYear());
    assertEquals("ISBN", book.getIsbn());
}
